        <h3 class="article__heading">01. Challenge</h3>

        <p>Cherie, Vree's founder, had an idea for a product that she wanted to validate, and was in the earliest stages her journey. She didn‚Äôt have a team, or a prototype, or a design‚Äîjust an idea and some personas. She conducted some light generative research and talked to some creative professionals in her network; but it was now time to test her idea and see if it was worth building. She came to thoughtbot to get validation on her idea and ultimately decide upon a path forward. We suggested a Product Design Sprint, to capture assumptions, ideate on possible solutions, and create a prototype to put in front of users.</p>

