        <h3 class="article__heading">03. Outcome</h3>

        <p>On the fourth day of the Sprint the other designer and I created a prototype asynchronously using Figma. We touched on all the assumptions we wanted to test, created a testing script, and finished our clickable prototype by the end of the day.</p>

        <div class="article__image-container article__image-container--stretch">
