        <p>Our prototype flow included three main ideas that we wanted feedback on. The first was providing users with a way to import images from various sources, like their Pinterest and Instagram accounts, and giving them the ability to sort them as they are imported. The second was giving them different ways to filter and search through a library of images. And finally, we wanted to see if they were interessed in creating and sharing moodboards with their selected images.</p>

